{"tid":1256503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國一間外貿公司因翻牆被罰","createTime":"2019-06-25T05:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T01:52:33.000Z","uid":1886,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"11ab19401cdd2e60111ab150de185e35b51519bc","tid":1256503,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"浙江省海寧市一家外貿公司近日擅自安裝翻牆軟件，並用以瀏覽外國網站，終被警方發現。該公司最後被判行政處罰，作為警告。 <br />\n<br />\n該公司由於業務需要，於今年4月由員工張珊（化名）在網上購買翻牆軟件。警方於一個月後巡查市內的外貿公司，因而揭發該公司的行為。 <br />\n<br />\n警方指，該公司擅自建立、使用非法定信道進行國際聯網，違反《中華人民共和國計算機信息網絡國際聯網管理暫行規定》。據指，翻牆軟件未獲得電信主管部門批准。而工信部已明確規定，未經批准，不得自行使用翻牆軟件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190615/bkn-20190615200532464-0615_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190615%2Fbkn-20190615200532464-0615_00952_001.html&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443mWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=23740b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190615/bkn-20190615200532464-0615_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"18fb5a79bf2822cad28c9ab3401d631bc479fab7","tid":1256503,"uid":18569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:10:47.000Z","msg":"咁唔愛國，竟然瀏覽外國網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b902787acb2326aa8e581514d46fedc5bb46ac","tid":1256503,"uid":83328,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:11:40.000Z","msg":"上外國網站大罪過上鹹網<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754ef83ee7083d50473af26442c5b4b700ef5771","tid":1256503,"uid":261699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13de83d9edee36957d04ac7eb2bb00250b31ae6e","tid":1256503,"uid":48234,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">問吓啲港豬想唔